01:05:12.204 --> 01:05:14.909
I'm so plugged up.

01:05:14.998 --> 01:05:18.663
Used to be as regular
as morning prayers.

01:05:18.752 --> 01:05:22.417
Matter of fact, I could
set my watch by my bowels.

