01:10:26.977 --> 01:10:29.978
I'm headin' for that smokehouse.

01:10:30.063 --> 01:10:32.389
And I'm ready to be
washed clean of my dirt,

01:10:32.483 --> 01:10:35.437
Yeah, Mae, you go
tend to him, - Mm-hm.

01:10:35.527 --> 01:10:36.558
