01:10:41.867 --> 01:10:43.860
Come on, get to bed,
- Now?

01:10:43.952 --> 01:10:47.487
Everybody to bed, Lila,
you stay with them kids.

01:10:47.581 --> 01:10:49.823
Get on up those stairs.

01:10:49.917 --> 01:10:51.743
