01:11:40.801 --> 01:11:45.130
And ride me all the way to China.

01:11:57.985 --> 01:11:59.395
You shy?

01:11:59.486 --> 01:12:02.156
Do you need a hand?
- No, Uh,,.

01:12:02.239 --> 01:12:05.489
Let's have a look and
see what we can muster.

01:12:06.285 --> 01:12:09.239
