01:12:47.117 --> 01:12:50.486
Thanks,
- God will judge you.

01:12:50.579 --> 01:12:55.241
Move out.
- Our lives are on your rotten soul,

01:12:55.334 --> 01:12:57.125
Mister?
- Your rotten soul.

01:12:57.211 --> 01:12:59.203
Shut your mouth.

01:13:01.131 --> 01:13:04.002
Pleasure doin' business with you, boys,
- Judas.

01:13:04.092 --> 01:13:05.752
Save your breath.

01:13:05.844 --> 01:13:08.631
You got a long walk
back to the fightin'.

01:13:14.061 --> 01:13:17.145
Ada Monroe and Ruby
Thewes, look at you both.

01:13:17.231 --> 01:13:18.559
