and dirt, Found a sack hid in the larder.

01:13:35.332 --> 01:13:38.001
Mmm, Thank you both.

01:13:38.085 --> 01:13:42.083
Ruby, I look forward
to this, We all do.

01:13:42.172 --> 01:13:43.750
Esco and me,

01:13:44.508 --> 01:13:47.592
