be real sorry he missed you.

01:14:10.450 --> 01:14:11.731
Yep,

01:14:16.415 --> 01:14:19.332
Strike you as odd?
- What?

01:14:19.418 --> 01:14:23.878
Stood at her front door,
- I know.

01:14:23.964 --> 01:14:28.044
Number one, I knowed that woman all my
life, I never stood outside her house.

01:14:28.135 --> 01:14:31.338
She'd let a wolf in if
it knocked at the door.

01:14:31.430 --> 01:14:33.173
Perhaps,,.

01:14:33.265 --> 01:14:35.554
