house, I could smell his pipe burnin',

01:14:41.565 --> 01:14:46.143
Number three, look at them fields,
- What about them?

01:14:46.236 --> 01:14:50.400
We come by here a week ago
and they was waist-high in hay.

01:14:50.491 --> 01:14:54.702
You tellin' me that's work
for one old man and his dog?

01:15:02.586 --> 01:15:04.744
Yankees. Yankees.

01:15:04.838 --> 01:15:07.460
Cavalry. Federal raiders.

01:15:07.549 --> 01:15:09.589
Just over that hill,

01:15:09.676 --> 01:15:12.677
Get those sacks of shit up that hill,
- Come on.

01:15:20.312 --> 01:15:24.891
Get those horses under cover,
If they see us, we're dead.

01:15:25.567 --> 01:15:28.402
Make a move, make a noise,,.

01:16:02.187 --> 01:16:04.559
I'm gettin' out of this.

01:16:04.648 --> 01:16:09.061
I'm not gettin' shot again for
some cause I don't believe in.

01:16:09.153 --> 01:16:10.896
Come on, let's go.

01:16:10.988 --> 01:16:12.815
Come on, They can't shoot, Come on.

01:16:17.077 --> 01:16:18.904
Keep goin'. Come on.

01:16:18.996 --> 01:16:21.072
Bayonets.

01:16:22.708 --> 01:16:24.416
Come on.

01:16:54.239 --> 01:16:58.700
Grab their boots and
rifles. Let's move on.

01:16:58.785 --> 01:17:00.825
Let's go.

01:17:16.428 --> 01:17:20.177
That scarecrow ain't gonna
frighten off no Yankee.

01:17:20.265 --> 01:17:22.887
Or are you tryin' to
make a man for yourself?

01:17:22.976 --> 01:17:24.554
