- Where's your little servant girl?

01:17:44.832 --> 01:17:48.699
Ruby, She tradin' off more
of your daddy's silver?

01:17:48.794 --> 01:17:51.249
Stop it.
- Her nose is in the butter.

01:17:51.338 --> 01:17:54.007
Her nose is right in your butter.

01:18:03.851 --> 01:18:06.389
This farm's got my name on it.

01:18:06.478 --> 01:18:10.061
You listenin', woman? You're
gonna need more than a scarecrow.

01:19:38.487 --> 01:19:40.479
Sal.

01:19:51.083 --> 01:19:53.159
Afternoon.

01:19:55.128 --> 01:19:58.580
Don't spread out, Why
are they spreadin' out?

01:19:58.674 --> 01:20:01.295
I never seen a man work a
field with a shotgun before.

01:20:01.385 --> 01:20:02.760
There's a war on.

01:20:02.845 --> 01:20:04.921
Get off my land,

01:20:05.848 --> 01:20:09.299
Your boys come home?
- Ain't seen my boys in four years.

01:20:09.393 --> 01:20:12.062
They're out fightin' other
boys, not old men and women.

01:20:12.146 --> 01:20:14.897
So you won't mind if we look around?

01:20:14.982 --> 01:20:17.224
'Cause we think they're here.

01:20:17.317 --> 01:20:20.022
We think you've got
'em hid up somewhere.

01:20:20.112 --> 01:20:24.275
What I gotta give you? Chicken? Lamb?

01:20:25.742 --> 01:20:27.367
Sure.

01:20:27.452 --> 01:20:30.619
The thing is, you've
only got one barrel.

01:20:30.706 --> 01:20:34.454
And there's five of us,
That's not a fair fight.

01:20:38.088 --> 01:20:40.294
King of kings.

01:20:41.300 --> 01:20:42.462
Hey.

01:20:43.886 --> 01:20:44.917
What was that?

01:20:45.762 --> 01:20:47.305
Aargh.

01:20:48.974 --> 01:20:52.841
