No.

01:22:56.059 --> 01:22:58.135
No.

01:22:59.688 --> 01:23:01.147
Oh, God, Sally?

01:23:01.231 --> 01:23:02.560
Ada.

01:23:04.193 --> 01:23:06.185
All right, all right.

01:23:08.822 --> 01:23:10.981
Darlin', what?

01:23:11.825 --> 01:23:14.826
She's sayin' 'Don't bother'. Go.

01:23:19.124 --> 01:23:21.247
Get her neck.

01:23:21.335 --> 01:23:23.908
Sally.
- Get her neck.

01:23:27.633 --> 01:23:31.084
This world won't stand long.

01:23:31.178 --> 01:23:33.254
God won't let it,,,

01:23:34.431 --> 01:23:37.432
stand this way long,

01:23:42.731 --> 01:23:48.686
How long have I been sleepin'?
