01:23:48.779 --> 01:23:52.693
I can't stop here,
- Sit down before you fall down.

01:23:52.783 --> 01:23:55.404
I'm a deserter.

01:23:55.494 --> 01:23:58.827
If they find me here,
things could be bad for you.

01:23:58.914 --> 01:24:01.535
What are they gonna do?
Cut short my young life?

01:24:10.425 --> 01:24:14.044
I've learned a person can pretty
much survive off of a goat.

01:24:14.138 --> 01:24:17.008
A goat gives you company,

01:24:17.099 --> 01:24:18.890
and milk,

01:24:18.976 --> 01:24:20.719
and cheese,

01:24:20.811 --> 01:24:23.563
and, when you need it,

01:24:23.647 --> 01:24:25.438
good meat.

01:24:28.360 --> 01:24:30.353
That's my beauty.

01:24:30.654 --> 01:24:32.860
There's my beauty.

01:24:33.490 --> 01:24:36.064
So you been fightin'.

01:24:38.829 --> 01:24:41.664
I could be at killin',,,

